The Tuck In Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt.
Featuring hand-drawn illustrations of an Australian favourite Fish and Chips.

The State Fish Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt.
Featuring hand-drawn illustrations of our favourite Australia Fish
G'day! This tote is made from 100% cotton featuring a hand-drawn illustration of a bunch of Australian proteas. Take yours to the supermarket and say no to plastic bags.
The G'day embroidered tee is a light-weight linen tee. Designed for a loose but feminine and flattering fit. Featuring an embroidered G'day motif.

The State Birds Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt. Featuring hand-drawn illustrations of the Australian bird emblem from each state with a contrast sky blue neckline and cuffs. Made from a soft vintage feel cotton jersey.

The Wattle Guide Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt. Featuring hand-drawn illustrations of the Australian floral emblem from each state with a contrast dusty green neckline and cuffs. Made from a soft vintage feel cotton jersey.

The Gday Protea Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt. Featuring a bold graphic type and hand-drawn illustration of Australian protea with a contrast dusty red rib neckline and cuffs. Made from a soft vintage feel cotton jersey.

The Luna Linen Shorts are a vintage-inspired style in a bold Australian bush floral-inspired print. Made in a soft mid-weighted linen, the shorts sit comfortably on the high waist skimming the hips with a straight leg. Generous curved pockets feature on the front. Designed to wear with the matching Luna Linen Top.

The Luna Linen Shorts are a vintage-inspired style in a rattan print. Made in a soft mid-weight linen, the shorts sit comfortably on the high waist skimming the hips with a straight leg. Curved pockets feature on the front. Designed to wear with the matching Luna Linen Top.

The Luna Linen Dress is a sleeveless shift dress in a vintage rattan inspired print. Made in a soft mid-weight linen, this style has a high neckline with bust shaping darts for a flattering A-line fit. The dress falls above the knee and curved front pockets.

The State Flora Tee is a signature RYDER vintage style t-shirt. Featuring hand-drawn illustrations of Australian flora from each state and a contrast dusty red rib neckline. Made from a soft vintage feel cotton jersey.
